  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the diced chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5-6 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced fernbrake-gosari and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic, grated ginger, paprika, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper. Stir well to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until the flavors have melded together.",
    "Fluff the royal couscous with a fork and place in a large serving dish.",
    "Add the cooked fernbrake-gosari and chicken mixture on top of the couscous.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley or cilantro, if desired.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
